itunes:summary:
Ross Patterson, Mat Best, Jarred Taylor, and Evan Hafer are joined by the "Lone Survivor" himself, Marcus Luttrell, as he talks about his illustrious career both in and out of the military. Marcus is one of the most inspiring people we know and it was great to finally sit down with him on the show. Amazing show.
